  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Reversing Environmental Degradation in Africa and Asia (REDAA) - developing innovative approaches to managing the natural environment, supporting livelihoods and protecting wildlife.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This programme focuses on addressing the challenge of environmental degradation in Africa and Asia - seeking to improve the condition of natural landscapes in ways that enable people and nature to thrive together.  REDAA will expand the technical knowledge and evidence base for environmental restoration and sustainable natural resources management in Africa and Asia; and develop innovative solutions that address serious environmental challenges and support the design and implementation of sustainable livelihoods strategies for local communities.</narrative>
  </description>
